articles.title: Are American Troops Fighting in Ukraine? What U.S. Intel Leaks Reveal - Newsweek
articles.description: Dozens of leaked U.S. intelligence documents about the war in Ukraine and other national security issues were found online last month.
articles.content:
A trove of leaked classified documents from the Defense Department suggests that more than a dozen American troops have been operating in Ukraine.
